snippet: A federal judge has overturned an Arizona law that sought to block state financing for Planned Parenthood health care clinics because the group also performs abortions.
abstract: Federal Judge Neil V Wake overturns Arizona law that sought to block state financing for Planned Parenthood health care clinics because group also performs abortions.
